---
/* S118 (K.3 prep) — Homepage disclaimer gate for the Kraken cutover windows.
   COLLAUDO_COMMS_GUIDELINES_v1 Step 1/3: during a cutover/switch window the
   homepage is REPLACED by a single disclaimer view ("we are going live on
   Kraken… stay tuned"), while the rest of the site (blog, diary, roadmap)
   stays reachable. Built as a REUSABLE TOGGLE (flag on/off + parametric
   text) because the same window repeats for BTC → SOL → BONK.

   Mechanics (zero-deploy, same pattern as project_status / Brief 86a):
   - Rendered SSR as a hidden, fixed, full-viewport OPAQUE overlay — no
     wrapping/hiding of the existing homepage content needed.
   - live-stats.ts reads public.site_flags (single row, anon read-only) at
     load: disclaimer_mode=true → set the parametric text + unhide.
   - Flip = `UPDATE site_flags SET disclaimer_mode=true, disclaimer_text=…`
     (SQL editor / MCP). No build, no deploy. Fase 1 ships it OFF.

   Known limits (accepted in the S118 plan): ~0.5-1s of normal homepage
   before the flag resolves (FOUC); crawlers/no-JS keep seeing the normal
   home (SSR fallbacks are neutral since S117); if Supabase itself is down
   the gate stays OFF (plan B: manual redeploy with a static page).
   The "curated image" from the guidelines is a pending asset (Max/CEO) —
   the art block below is its placeholder. */
---

<div
  id="disclaimer-gate"
  class="fixed inset-0 z-[100] hidden overflow-y-auto"
  style="background-color: var(--color-bg);"
  aria-hidden="true"
>
  <div class="flex min-h-full flex-col items-center justify-center px-4 py-12">

    <div class="w-full max-w-xl rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface
                p-8 text-center shadow-sticker sm:p-10">

      {/* status badge — same sticker grammar as the hero badge */}
      <div class="mx-auto mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border
                  border-border bg-panel px-3 py-1 font-mono text-[10.5px] font-bold
                  uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-text-muted">
        <span class="inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 animate-pulse rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
        <span>Cutover in progress</span>
      </div>

      {/* art placeholder — swap for the curated image when it exists */}
      <div class="mx-auto mb-6 flex h-20 w-20 items-center justify-center
                  rounded-2xl bg-primary-soft text-4xl" aria-hidden="true">
        🐙
      </div>

      <h1 class="font-display text-[26px] font-extrabold leading-[1.15]
                 tracking-[-0.02em] text-text sm:text-[30px]">
        The machine is switching gears.
      </h1>

      {/* parametric message — filled from site_flags.disclaimer_text */}
      <p id="disclaimer-gate-text"
         class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-md text-[15px] leading-[1.65] text-text-dim">
        We are going live on Kraken to test our bots — stay tuned!
      </p>

      <p class="mt-6 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-text-muted">
        The rest of the site is open as usual
      </p>

      <nav class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-5 gap-y-2
                  text-[13.5px] font-semibold text-primary">
        <a href="/blog/" class="hover:underline">Blog</a>
        <a href="/library/" class="hover:underline">Library</a>
        <a href="/roadmap/" class="hover:underline">Roadmap</a>
        <a href="/howwework/" class="hover:underline">How we work</a>
      </nav>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
